{"id":162,"date":"2017-07-20T13:27:40","date_gmt":"2017-07-20T13:27:40","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/hoodbuilder.dev\/?page_id=162"},"modified":"2023-11-19T05:22:06","modified_gmt":"2023-11-19T05:22:06","slug":"construction","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/restaurant-services\/construction\/","title":{"rendered":"Commercial Kitchen &#038; Restaurant Construction"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_row css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1500556319702{background-color: #eeeeec !important;}&#8221;][vc_column offset=&#8221;vc_col-lg-offset-2 vc_col-lg-8 vc_col-md-offset-1 vc_col-md-10&#8243;]<div class=\"ult-spacer spacer-685e552102cf5\" data-id=\"685e552102cf5\" data-height=\"90\" data-height-mobile=\"70\" data-height-tab=\"\" data-height-tab-portrait=\"\" data-height-mobile-landscape=\"70\" style=\"clear:both;display:block;\"><\/div>[vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"big-para-blue\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hood Builder offers <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/general-contracting\/\">turnkey restaurant construction<\/a> to clients throughout Denver, CO. We have assembled an excellent team of electrical, mechanical, and structural experts, as well as restaurant design contractors. All of these professions have a common goal: To ensure your satisfaction while keeping to your timetable and budget. As a business owner looking to build the finest restaurant in town, you should never expect anything less.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"tel:+1-303-777-7720\" style=\"padding: 10px 20px 10px 20px; background-color: #0067ab;\">Free Quote 303-777-7720<\/a><\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text]<div class=\"ult-spacer spacer-685e552102d0e\" data-id=\"685e552102d0e\" data-height=\"60\" data-height-mobile=\"40\" data-height-tab=\"\" data-height-tab-portrait=\"\" data-height-mobile-landscape=\"40\" style=\"clear:both;display:block;\"><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column]<div class=\"ult-spacer spacer-685e552102d1d\" data-id=\"685e552102d1d\" data-height=\"90\" data-height-mobile=\"70\" data-height-tab=\"\" data-height-tab-portrait=\"\" data-height-mobile-landscape=\"70\" style=\"clear:both;display:block;\"><\/div>[\/vc_column][vc_column offset=&#8221;vc_col-lg-7 vc_col-md-7&#8243;][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We are confident that you will come to prefer us for our affordable pricing and the quality services we provide. If you are looking for a one-stop-shop for all your restaurant construction needs, we encourage you to call Hood Builder today.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>We Get Your Needs<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Send us a restaurant construction request, and we will provide you with a fast and honest quote. We can only begin your project and satisfy your requirements when we completely understanding your commercial contracting needs. Call and let us know how we can help, as we remain confident that we can exceed all of your expectations.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"display: inline;\"><b>Restaurant preconstruction: <\/b><\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; display: inline;\">Preparation is key when it comes to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/clients\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">restaurant construction projects<\/span><\/a> of all sizes. We manage the construction site and all personnel while ensuring your plans, drawings, and vision are all in order for an efficient design-build job.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"display: inline;\"><b>Restaurant construction: <\/b><\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; display: inline;\">You never have to worry when you hire Hood Builder to manage your restaurant construction site. We take care of all permits and legalities while ensuring safety as we get the job done right the first time around. We only provide top-notch quality while leaving no mess behind.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"display: inline;\"><b>Restaurant Design\/build services: <\/b><\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; display: inline;\">We take care of all aspects of the design-build process. If you want turnkey restaurant services, so all you have to do is think up a plan and then show up to pick up the keys, we can accommodate you.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"display: inline;\"><b>Full construction management: <\/b><\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; display: inline;\">We allow you to take a hands-off approach to opening your new restaurant. From managing our restaurant contractors and interior designers to the janitorial staff that cleans up after we\u2019re done, you never have to worry about a thing.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In all the years that we\u2019ve been helping Denver customers, we have worked with the biggest names in the restaurant industry. These include Pizza Hut and McDonald\u2019s, Applebee\u2019s and Burger King, and Subway. You can always trust us to come through for all your electrical, mechanical, structural, and fire protection needs.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>Plans, Permits, Full Construction &amp; Remodeling Services<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Building a new restaurant always starts with a clear vision. Then, a set of plans must be drawn up. Unless you have experience <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/restaurant-services\/design\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">planning and designing restaurants<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, you might want to let the professionals do the job for you.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">At Hood Builder, we have a team of architects, designers, and restaurant construction professionals who draw up plans for establishments like yours for a living. These experts have worked with all types of concepts and designs. You would be amazed at how they can help you bring your vision of the ideal restaurant together, even if you only have a tiny inkling of what the final product will look like.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">From the initial concept of your restaurant design to the drawing up of the actual plans, our restaurant design-build team can handle everything. Our stellar reputation speaks for itself. When you work with us, you will soon realize why we\u2019re the preferred restaurant construction service in the Denver areas.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If a restaurant renovation is the order of the day, we will develop a plan to make the most of your space while avoiding your establishment\u2019s workflow. You are sure to find our services customer-friendly while freeing you of all stress.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hood Builder and our <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/about-us\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">talented team of restaurant designers<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and contractors will provide you with high levels of attention to detail and superb performance while keeping to your budget and schedule. Then, all you have to do is show up, take the keys, and your restaurant can open to much fanfare as locals come from far and wide to see your newly remodeled restaurant.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>For a full and honest quote, <\/b><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/contact-us\/\"><b>contact Hood Builder<\/b><\/a><b> today.<\/b><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"tel:+1-303-777-7720\" style=\"padding: 10px 20px 10px 20px; background-color: #0067ab;\">Free Quote 303-777-7720<\/a><\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column offset=&#8221;vc_col-lg-offset-1 vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-offset-1 vc_col-md-4&#8243;][vc_wp_custommenu nav_menu=&#8221;9&#8243; el_class=&#8221;wps-sidebar-related-links&#8221; title=&#8221;Related Links&#8221;]<div class=\"templatera_shortcode\"><div id=\"\" class=\"wps-row-container vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid